ai-patthana15.51:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma: allows unintelligent in the Khadehaka, and constantly preciously:
ai-patthana15.51:0.3_0: Talking for profitable, they don’t attack themselves,
ai-patthana15.51:1.1_0: Not grasping arises dependent on those skillful things, and those who don’t give rise to the unskillful.
ai-patthana15.51:2.1_0: Not grasping arises in those who are unskillful, or unskillful.
ai-patthana15.51:2.1_3: What is the same as worthless?
ai-patthana15.51:3.1_0: The group of twelve on large teeth is finished.
